beer.beer_description:
‘vibes on toast’ // bière de garde // barrel fermented // 6.7%

Production time / 12 months

Primary fermentation occurred in a puncheon and a barrique for 10 months with a blend of lager, saison yeast and brett. lambicus.

Packaged on March 6th 2022 and bottle conditioned for 9 weeks.

The aroma is very warm and comforting. Elements of cherry cola, burnt toffee & pinot noir.
The palate is light but it carry's a gorgeous depth and richness with it. Spice, slightly burnt toast and port royal.
